<br>
<br>
&quot;Also, I think rains are faster blasts at most (all?) levels against 2 mobs in terms of damage / <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> cast</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> time&quot;<br>
<br>
If you're chain nuking for a duration of time it doesn't matter if the damage is dealt all at once or not, as long as the damage is dealt before you're done nuking.<br>
<br>
Example:<br>
<br>
You have a lvl 60 wizard that has 30 seconds to chain nuke against 2 mobs.<br>
<br>
(with a 2.2 estimate of the ungrey time)<br>
<br>
(a) Only pillars:<br>
3 * Pillar of Flame and 2 * Pillar of Lightning deals 9104 damage in 27.3 seconds. (for 1780 mana)<br>
<br>
(b) Mixed:<br>
The wizard casts all 3 50+ rain spells then finishes off with Pillar of Flame. He finishes casting after 26.1 seconds, the last wave of the last rain hits at 26.9 seconds, and deals a total of 9644 damage. (for 1589 mana)<br>
<br>
<br>
Also, due to the damage over time nature, if you can anticipate the time interval in which you'll be nuking (such as the 10 seconds it takes a mob to complete heal), you can start casting much earlier and pack some extra waves of rain into that interval.<br>
<br>
Arlina <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.kestrelarts.com/images/grimicon.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/25/01 8:22:37 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/grimmy.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Argument for the sake of</span><hr size=1> &quot;By claiming that AE rains are inferior across the board, you are claiming that the lvl 44 rain is inferior to the lvl 34 pillar on two targets.&quot;<br>
<br>
Actually, that's your assumption.  I'd think everyone else who read it understood what I said fine, that each comparison of similar levels shows the AE Rain spell to be inferior.  The only reason I can imagine you'd come up with this interperetation is the desire to argue.<br>
<br>
&quot;Also, I think rains are faster blasts at most (all?) levels against 2 mobs in terms of damage / cast time<br>
<br>
&quot;If you're chain nuking for a duration of time it doesn't matter if the damage is dealt all at once or not, as long as the damage is dealt before you're done nuking.&quot;<br>
<br>
On tuesdays with a full moon against fire resistant creatures in the Karanas you can stun more often with an Al'Kabor frost spiral than a fire spiral.  You sound like a baseball statistician.  <br>
<br>
AE Rain spells take longer to have their full effect than pillar spells.  Pillar spells do nearly the same or more damage than the closest AE Rain spell AND are resisted less often AND can't be walked out of AND take effect immediately.  What about that strikes you as being superior?<br>
<br>
I can concoct a scenario where casting Al'Kabor spells is superior to casting any other spell you have, but does that make them better?  This is silly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6531.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6566.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6414.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6414.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6414.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6414.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm28">The Library<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm25">Share Your Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm18">Admin<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm19">Soloing<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm20">AE Kiting<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm21">AE Grouping<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm2">General Quests<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm5">Staff of the Four - Epic Quest<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm26">Circlet of the Falinkan<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm23">Duties for the Crown<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm31">Fusibility Research<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm15">Hsagra's Wrath<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm12">Kael Drakkal Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm14">Skyshrine Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm7">Frostbeards Armor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm9">Phenocryst's Focus<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm17">Plane of Sky<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm16">Porlos' Fury<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm13">Rough Silver Chain<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm24">Staff of the Wheel - Ice Comet<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm11">Velium Chill of Al'Kabor<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm6">Tome of Ages Quest<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm29">Translocational Suppressions<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm30">Veeshan's Peak Key</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table></form></td></tr></table><br><font color=#ffffff>- </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation>Graffë's Wizard Discussion</a><font color=#ffffff> - </font><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1>General Dis